    All I ask is that you let me know what you think of it, and of course
    of any Bugs - If you want to send monetary gifts then all the
    better!!!


    When you send in your @{"RegistrationáForm" link "RegForm" 0}, I'll send you an unrestricted
    version of Diffmaker, personalised with your Details - And, If I
    decide to add some features to it, I'll send you any unrestricted
    updates.


    So - What is restricted about the Unregistered Version of Diffmaker?
    --------------------------------------------------------------------


    It hasn't got your personalised details in it, and the main restriction
    is that it will only Compare Nodelists less than 10k in size.


    Please Do send the registration form to me - It will let me know that
    it has all been worthwhile!!!!



