@node "Future" "The Future  "


                              THE FUTURE
                              ----------


    Well, if I get enough interest in Diffmaker, I would like to try and
    improve the speed of it. At the moment (depending on the number of
    changes), it will handle a 5k nodelist on my Unaccelerated A1200 in
    around 30 seconds - Archived up and everything!!

    However, I tried the Region 25 Fidonet Nodelist and that took over one
    and a half hours!!! :(((

    I do have a few ideas for speeding it up, but they'll have to wait
    till I see what the response is....

    Also, I would like to code a complete Suite of Fidonet Utilities -
    Keep an eye out, eh? ;))


                              --ooOOoo--
@endnode

